## ðŸŽ¨ The Pattern

### Design (.ui.qml)
```qml
// Pure UI - No Logic
Rectangle {
    TextField {
        placeholderText: "Username"
    }
    Button {
        text: "Login"
        highlighted: true
    }
}
```

### Implementation (.qml)
```qml
// Clean Logic
LoginPanelGUI {
    onLoginClicked: {
        rootStore.loginStore.login(
            username, password
        )
    }
}
```

